    "description": "<br><br>闪电战中尉围困了这座城市，你的工作是摧毁他的部队。射击，躲避和升级你的喷气式飞机，并尝试接受这个挑战！燃烧的天空是一个免费，无尽的复古shmup，它将带你回到街机时代，现代化的图形和游戏玩法！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290190/extras/91ded3cff17fef1bc2efa47c1c84a816.poster.avif?t=1725479401\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290190/extras/91ded3cff17fef1bc2efa47c1c84a816.webm?t=1725479401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290190/extras/91ded3cff17fef1bc2efa47c1c84a816.mp4?t=1725479401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>冲破一波又一波的敌人，改进你的喷气式飞机，并为其配备多种可用武器之一！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290190/extras/a3160c49a4d9c9451529c1aa172bac29.poster.avif?t=1725479401\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290190/extras/a3160c49a4d9c9451529c1aa172bac29.webm?t=1725479401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290190/extras/a3160c49a4d9c9451529c1aa172bac29.mp4?t=1725479401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>击败闪电战中尉，强大的战争机器，以及血梅斯特将军的军队！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290190/extras/bce7180f0138aa62f159c39538cb0946.poster.avif?t=1725479401\" width=606 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290190/extras/bce7180f0138aa62f159c39538cb0946.webm?t=1725479401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290190/extras/bce7180f0138aa62f159c39538cb0946.mp4?t=1725479401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>当您需要快速乐趣时，非常适合玩！这是一封写给 80 年代街机游戏的简短而自由的情书。灵感来自 1942、河流突袭、雷电等经典作品。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290190/extras/672348f816d94035bd0a279d28ff5e9b.poster.avif?t=1725479401\" width=606 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290190/extras/672348f816d94035bd0a279d28ff5e9b.webm?t=1725479401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290190/extras/672348f816d94035bd0a279d28ff5e9b.mp4?t=1725479401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>特征<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>美丽的3D体素图形;<br></li><li>无休止的程序生成游戏玩法;<br></li><li>各种独特的敌人，武器和极具挑战性的BOSS战;<br></li><li>原创音乐</li></ul>",
